name: Tuning Contest WAD
description: This is a compilation of all the contest wads which were sent to the contest held in iddqd.ru and doomworld.com. Read the rules_e.html To play this PWAD file, unzip it into the directory with your PWADs then start: glboom-plus.exe -file freak4.wad -complevel 11 (or higher) or zdoom.exe -file freak4.wad
